    <item>
      <title>哈佛大学向抗议者发出最后通牒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/harvard-issues-ultimatum-to-protesters-over-encampment-in-yard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学临时校长艾伦·加伯告诉抗议者，他们需要结束在哈佛庭院的营地，否则将面临包括停学在内的后果，因为毕业典礼临近，校园内持续紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/harvard-issues-ultimatum-to-protesters-over-encampment-in-yard</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国誓言保卫波罗的海国家免受俄罗斯袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/germany-vows-to-defend-baltic-nations-in-event-of-russian-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨承诺在俄罗斯发动袭击时保卫德国的三个波罗的海北约盟国，并在 2027 年底前完成在立陶宛建立常设旅的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/germany-vows-to-defend-baltic-nations-in-event-of-russian-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 14:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟计划在欧洲公投前禁止俄罗斯向各方提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/eu-aims-to-sanction-russian-political-cash-before-european-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟提议禁止政党、智库和其他团体接受俄罗斯的资助，作为下一轮制裁的一部分，旨在惩罚莫斯科对乌克兰的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/eu-aims-to-sanction-russian-political-cash-before-european-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 14:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
